
********************************************************************************

                QCD simulations with open boundary conditions

********************************************************************************

Simulation programs

qcd1        HMC simulation program for QCD with Wilson quarks and
            open boundary conditions

qcd2        HMC simulation program for QCD with Wilson quarks and
            Schroedinger functional boundary conditions

ym1         HMC simulation program for the SU(3) gauge theory with
            open boundary conditions


Measurement programs

ms1         Measurement of reweighting factors

ms2         Computation of the spectral range of the hermitian 
            Dirac operator

ms3         Computation of Wilson flow observables

ms4         Computation of quark propagators


Directories

examples    Examples of valid input parameter files

